reviewText: A great informative story of a talented musician, fantastic original songwriter and individual that has embraced her roots and is genuine and fearless in her expression of beliefs. Worth veiwing even if not a fan. The Bill Cosby endorsements seem a little creepy and outdated given recent publicity on the man, however I'm sure they were genuine in this case. A true original.

Very interesting and very informative study of a great North American treasure.
An in-depth summary of someone's life who got shafted for doing what she felt was right.
Wish more people had access to this video. She deserves much more recognition than she has received.
A very informative DVD-shipped fast..great purchase
